
#include<iostream>
#include<string>
using namespace std;
int cprimes[100001];
bool primes[100001];
int winssecond[100001];
bool winner[100001];
int main()
{
	for(int i=2;i<=100000;i++)
				{
					if(cprimes[i]==0){primes[i]=true;
					for(int j=i;j<=100000;j+=i)
					{
						cprimes[j]++;
					}}
					
				}
	int c=0;
				winssecond[c++]=0;
				winssecond[c++]=1;
				for(int i=2;i<=100000;i++)
				{
					bool wins=true;
					for(int j=0;j<c;j++)
					{
						if(primes[i-winssecond[j]]||cprimes[i-winssecond[j]]==2)
						{
							wins=false;
							break;
						}
					}
					
					if(wins)
					{	
						winssecond[c++]=i;
					
					}	
				}
				
				for(int i=0;i<c;i++)winner[winssecond[i]]=true;
				int t,N;
				cin>>t;				
				string k;
				while(t--)
				{
					cin>>k;
					cin>>N;
					if(winner[N])
					{
						if(k[0]=='S')
							printf("Pre\n");
						else
							printf("Sak\n");	
					}
					else
					{
						
						if(k[0]!='S')
							printf("Pre\n");
						else
							printf("Sak\n");	
					}
				}

}
